@node "Intro" "Introduction"
@next "Requirements"
@prev "Main"

                             Introduction

     I created this program in order to keep track of my prescriptions and
refills. I decided to release it because I'm sure there are many people who
may find it handy. 
     Its' use is pretty self-explanatory, but I have included full
instructions. Enjoy!
@endnode

@node "Requirements" "Requirements"
@next "Features"
@prev "Intro"

                        Requirements

     This product was developed using CanDo 2.511, an A1200 with 2 Megs Chip/4
Megs Fast RAM, Amiga DOS 3.1,  a 128 Meg hard drive, and lots of Diet Coke
:).
     In order to use it, you'll need:

     *    1 Meg RAM
     *    WB 2.1 (at least)
     *    A floppy or hard drive
     *    CanDo.library V2.511

That's it.

@endnode

